ution> <id>generate</id> <goals> <goal>generate</goal> </goals> <phase>process-classes</phase> </execution> </executions> </plugin>\n\nSee plugin configuration docs for all configuration properties.\n\n## Supported annotations\n\n  * AssertFalse\n  * AssertTrue\n  * DecimalMax - Not yet implemented\n  * DecimalMin - Not yet implemented\n  * Digits - Not yet implemented\n  * Email\n  * Future - Not yet implemented\n  * FutureOrPresent - Not yet implemented\n  * Max\n  * Min\n  * Negative\n  * NegativeOrZero\n  * NotBlank\n  * NotEmpty\n  * NotNull\n  * Null - Not yet implemented\n  * Past - Not yet implemented\n  * PastOrPresent - Not yet implemented\n  * Pattern\n\n    * No transformation is made to the regex pattern string. Keep in mind that the Java and JavaScript regex engines are not identical. The only flags supported are:\n\n      * CASE_INSENSITIVE (/i)\n      * MULTILINE (/m)\n      * DOTALL (/s)\n    * All other flags are ignored\n  * Positive\n  * PositiveOrZero\n  * Size\n\n## About\n\nConvert POJOs to Zod schemas\n\njava-to-zod.ivan.sh/java-to-zod-maven-plugin/generate-mojo.html\n\n### Resources\n\nReadme\n\n### License\n\nApache-2.0 license\n\nActivity\n\n### Stars\n\n1 star\n\n### Watchers\n\n1 watching\n\n### Forks\n\n0 forks\n\nReport repository\n\n## Releases\n\n15 tags\n\n## Packages 0\n\nNo packages published\n\n## Contributors 2\n\n  * ivangreene Ivan Greene\n  * actions-user\n\n## Languages\n\n  * Java 85.2%\n  * JavaScript 14.6%\n  * Makefile 0.2%\n\n## Footer\n\n\u00a9 2024 GitHub, Inc.\n\nYou can\u2019t perform that action at this time.\n\n", "frontpage": false}
